ave lessons</tr_> in grammar, rhetoric, politics, mathematics, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">for money</tr_>, such as Prodicus, Gorgias, Protagoras, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὴν σοφίαν τοὺς ἀργυρίου τῷ βουλομένῳ πωλοῦντας σοφιστὰς ἀποκαλοῦσιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:6:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mem.\">Mem.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.6.13</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg014.perseus-grc1:13:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyn.\">Cyn.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.8</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.38</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg022:31\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prt.\">Prt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">31</biblScope> </bibl> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg022:3c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3c</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg021:271c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Euthd.\">Euthd.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">271c</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg019:186c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ La.\">La.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">186c</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg024:85b\" default=